508
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:44,429
She have any family? Might
be time to notify next of kin...

509
00:37:44,496 --> 00:37:47,091
I read about a clinical rescue
therapy trial, the chill study.

510
00:37:47,165 --> 00:37:49,532
She's a good candidate,
no cytokine storm,

511
00:37:49,601 --> 00:37:52,093
her troponin's low, so
are LFTs and creatinine.

512
00:37:52,170 --> 00:37:53,433
Her organs are in good shape.

513
00:37:53,505 --> 00:37:56,475
