virtually every muscle in her body?

514
00:37:57,175 --> 00:37:59,940
Lowering the temperature
reduces her inflammatory response

515
00:38:00,011 --> 00:38:04,278
and her need for oxygen. And it's
better than calling her next of kin.

516
00:38:04,349 --> 00:38:08,116
